<title>“今天，所有VC的会上都在谈Sora”</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E2%80%9C%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89VC%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8A%E9%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E8%B0%88Sora%E2%80%9D</link>
<content:encoded>&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;rich_media_thumb_wrp&quot; id=&quot;media&quot;&gt;

                &lt;img class=&quot;rich_media_thumb&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/b2YlTLuGbKAic2exUD4OFIUOBmvseZXfAxQXzRkS1cLeeoeQsMJmib6rCylyU1g8xAMkHd6NqxPl6X6pXtlHNCBg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg?imageView2/1/w/600&quot; /&gt;
